cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CL 

This paper deals with image-to-image translation, specifically in the facial image domain. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the use of prior knowledge and normalization methods, which are common techniques in machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The paper also involves perceptual realism, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
